    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You captivated us and now"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We follow in Your train."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are Your people, You’re our God."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In us do rule and reign."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You are the man upon the throne"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Set there by God alone."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God planned and willed that You be Head,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord of all made known."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Those God foreknew, He set apart"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be conformed to You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That You would be His firstborn Son"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And we Your brothers true."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You conquered death and rose with might"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ascending to the height."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You carry out God’s will on earth,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Enthroned in glory bright."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, as the God-exalted man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The ruler of all kings,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your government fulfills God’s plan,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And utmost headship brings."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You, as God’s heir, uphold all things."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our heart in worship sings."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You make God’s substance known by all"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As from Your throne life springs."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our pioneer and forerunner,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You clearly cut the way"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Unto God’s throne and reign by life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To this, “Amen,” we say."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You take the lead, we follow You."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No other way will do,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For God intends to glorify"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And seat us there with You."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Under the ruling of Your life,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We too will reign as kings,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Saved by Your grace abundantly,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Upheld on eagle’s wings."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s gift of righteousness received"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By us who have believed,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll testify eternally"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your rule is all we need."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
